Package fi.tuni.swdesign.group3.gui.view

Class DataTab

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.control.Tab
fi.tuni.swdesign.group3.gui.view.DataTab
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
Direct Known Subclasses:
CombinedDataTab, RoadDataTab, WeatherDataTab
public abstract class DataTab extends javafx.scene.control.Tab
An abstract base class for a tab in which the data parameters are set and the data is visualized.
Author:
Lauri Puoskari
